org.springframework.cloud.netflix.turbine

Class EurekaInstanceDiscovery

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.cloud.netflix.turbine.CommonsInstanceDiscovery
      • org.springframework.cloud.netflix.turbine.EurekaInstanceDiscovery
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.netflix.turbine.discovery.InstanceDiscovery

    public class EurekaInstanceDiscovery
extends CommonsInstanceDiscovery
    Class that encapsulates an InstanceDiscovery implementation that uses Eureka (see https://github.com/Netflix/eureka) The plugin requires a list of applications configured. It then queries the set of instances for each application. Instance information retrieved from Eureka must be translated to something that Turbine can understand i.e the Instance class.

    All the logic to perform this translation can be overriden here, so that you can provide your own implementation if needed.

    Author:
    Spencer Gibb
